ilm)|Badlapur]]''\n| [[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actor]]\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Zee Cine Awards]]\n| [[Bajrangi Bhaijaan]]''\n| [[Zee Cine Award for Best Actor in a Comic Role]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| ''[[Badlapur (film)|Badlapur]]''\n| [[Zee Cine Award for Best Performance in a Negative Role]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2018\n|[[Filmfare Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" |''[[Mom (film)|Mom]]''\n|[[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actor]]\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n|[[IIFA Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Best Performance in a Supporting Role (Male)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iifa.com/awards2018 |title=IIFA Awards 2018 Winners |publisher=[[International Indian Film Academy Awards|IIFA]]}}</ref>\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|[[GQ Men of the Year Awards|GQ Men of the Year]]\n|\n|-\n| [[Asia Pacific Screen Awards]]\n| [[Manto (2018 film)|Manto]]\n| Best Performance By An Actor<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiawest.com/entertainment/bollywood/nandita-das-nawazuddin-siddiqui-awarded-at-asia-pacific-screen-awards/article_78f39b70-f4c6-11e8-a743-ef17c9e71484.html|title=Nandita Das, Nawazuddin Siddiqui Awarded at Asia Pacific Screen Awards|last=IANS|website=India West}}</ref>\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|[[IReel Awards]]\n|''[[Sacred Games (TV series)|Sacred Games]]''\n|Best Actor (Drama)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.news18.com/news/movies/news18-ireel-awards-2018-check-out-the-complete-list-of-winners-here-1870033.html|title=News18 iReel Awards 2018: Check Out the Complete List of Winners Here|website=News18|access-date=2019-09-21}}</ref>\n|{{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|2019\n| [[Filmfare Awards]]\n| [[Manto (2018 film)|Manto]]\n| Best Actor (Critics)\n|{{Nom}}\n|}\n\n=== International recognition ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Festival / Award\n!Film \n!Category\n!Result\n|-\n|2012\n|[[Asian Film Awards]]\n|[[Talaash: The Answer Lies Within|Talaash]]: The answer lies within\n|Asian Film award for best supporting actor<ref>{{Citation|title=Talaash - IMDb|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1787988/awards|access-date=2019-12-25}}</ref>\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|2012\n|\u201cTHUMBSUP TROPHY\u201d by [[Roger Ebert|Mr.Roger Ebert]]\n|Patang\n|\n|\n|-\n|2012\n|[[New York Film Festival|NYIFF]]\n|[[Dekh Indian Circus]]\n|Award for best actor<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.news18.com/news/india/dekh-indian-circus-nawazuddin-plays-a-mute-man-503150.html|title=Dekh Indian Circus: Nawazuddin plays a mute man|website=News18|access-date=2019-12-25}}</ref>\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|2013\n|[[Asia-Pacific Film Festival|Asia Pacific Film Festival]]\n|[[The Lunchbox]]\n|Best Supporting actor<ref>{{Citation|title=Dabba - IMDb|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2350496/awards|access-date=2019-12-25}}</ref>\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|2014\n|[[Chicago International Film Festival|Chicago South Asian Film Festival]]\n|\n|Honored for \u2018outstanding achievement\u2019 in cinema<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.news18.com/news/india/nawazuddin-siddiqui-to-be-honoured-at-the-chicago-south-asian-film-festival-for-outstanding-achievement-in-cinema-713303.html|title=Nawazuddin Siddiqui to be honoured at the Chicago South Asian Film Festival for 'outstanding achievement' in cinema|website=News18|access-date=2019-12-25}}</ref>\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|2016\n|FANCINE festival de cine fantastic de la Universidad de la Malaga\n|[[Raman Raghav 2.0]]\n|Official Jury Prize<ref>{{Citation|title=Raman Raghav 2.0 - IMDb|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt5662932/awards|access-date=2019-12-25}}</ref>\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|2016\n|[[Asia Pacific Screen Awards]]\n|[[Raman Raghav 2.0]]\n|Best performance by an actor<ref>{{Citation|title=Raman Raghav 2.0 - IMDb|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt5662932/awards|access-date=2019-12-25}}</ref>\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|2017\n|[[New York Film Festival|NYIFF]]\n|[[Haraamkhor]]\n|Best Actor<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/nawazuddin-siddiqui-haramkhor-new-york-film-festival-shlok-sharma-best-actor-award-252568-2015-05-12|title=Nawazuddin Siddiqui: Honoured to rec